caption:
The War for the Dawn by the wonderful @icesalamander

“Why do the gods make kings and queens, if not to protect the ones who can’t protect themselves?“  –Daenerys III, A Storm of Swords

We were never meant to do this alone.

Merry Christmas, @daeyton! 🎄🌟🎁 I commissioned this fanart for you for the Jonerys Secret Santa @iceandfiresource event! summary:
To my dearest readers and followers,
As we come to the end of another chaotic year, I just wanted to take this opportunity to...
body:
Merry Christmas!

To my dearest readers and followers,

As we come to the end of another chaotic year, I just wanted to take this opportunity to thank each and everyone for your support and encouragement through it all.

In case some of you didn’t know, I was unjustly uprooted from a place I had called home for 22 years without warning, but not before being made to spend a month in a detention center. (Memories I want erased asap)

I was in the midst of writing Eye of the Storm, and wondered if that would ever get completed. But by the grace of God, I was able to do so, and not only that, I managed to start a new story - Shadows - and completed that considering all the BS happening around me.

As always, I would not have done that without your support. Fandom might have its issues, but at least we can all agree that we are fans first and foremost, and our love for the show (and books) is what drives us everyday.

So here’s wishing you all a very wonderful Christmas and a much happier and better 2019!

Be good to each other!
